						<p>Fragmentary. Seems to register a gift of land in Rājarāja-vaḷanāḍu, the <hi rend="italic">nāyakkattaṉam</hi> of Tirumalaidēva-Mahārāja, as an offering of Cheṉṉappanāyakkar. The details of the date except for <hi rend="bold">Dhanus, śu. Tiruvādirai,</hi> are lost.</p>						

